<![CDATA[<FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif">Hello {!Contact.FirstName},</SPAN><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif">I wanted to send you a brief introduction to Wright Express prior to calling you.</SPAN><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif">We are B2B payments specialist and a leading provider of single use virtual card technology to the online travel industry.&nbsp; We provide the solution that powers the supplier payment process for many of the world’s top online travel agents.</SPAN><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif">Key benefits of our solution include – <SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Control, Information and Automation</SPAN>.</SPAN><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"><BR style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"></FONT>
<UL>
