<LI><FONT size=3><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: Times New Roman,Times,Serif"><SPAN style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">Information</SPAN>: Capture bespoke data specific to booking e.g.&nbsp;hotel name, reservation number, cost centre&nbsp;to ensure that all payments reconcile to each order.</SPAN></FONT>
